snippet.title: Dragonward - PC Game Review - UT
snippet.description:
*Update: Turns out lag was caused by my video capture software. So most likely won't be a problem to most!*An interesting streamlining of the RPG genre in Dragonward! Support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/umbrellaterms
Buy me a coffee: https://www.Ko-fi.com/umbrellaterms

Feedback on the video is always appreciated!

Itch.io Game Page: https://biterkid.itch.io/dragonward
